= Letsie III (萊齊耶三世) =
Mntucing hngkawas 1963 idas 7 jiyax 17 ka Letsie III ga, empklaw ka hiya.

Bukung klwaan [[Lesotho]] ta sayang o kiya ka Letsie III, pnaah hngkawas 1996 idas 2 jiyax 7 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.

